Nozibele Nyalambisa bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa na-eje ozi dị ka onye African National Congress Member nke Eastern Cape Provincial Legislature kemgbe 2019.
Nyalambisa jere ozi dị ka onye nnọchi anya African National Congress na Amathole District Municipality site na Mbhashe Local Municipality.

Nyalambisa nọ n'ọnọdụ nke iri atọ na asaa na ndepụta ndị ANC maka ntuli aka ndị omeiwu nke Eastern Cape Provincial na 8 Mee 2019. A họpụtara ya dịka ANC meriri oche 44. A ṅụrụ ya iyi dị ka onye otu Eastern Cape Provincial Legislature na 22 Mee
Ọ na-anọdụ ugbu a na Kọmitii Mmepe Ime Obodo na Mgbanwe Ala na Kọmiti Ahụike.
Àtụ:Members of the Eastern Cape Provincial Legislature
